            <title><![CDATA[Russia pounds Kyiv with missiles and drones after Ukraine's strikes on oil infrastructure]]></title>
            <link>https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/russia-pounds-kyiv-with-missiles-and-drones-after-ukraines-strikes-on-oil-infrastructure</link>
            <description><![CDATA[Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy promised heavy retaliation after an all-night barrage of Russian missiles and drones killed at least 25 in Kyiv. Ukraine has been launching mass drone attacks deep into Russia, targeting military installations and refineries. Russia has suffered as a result, with fuel shortages reported throughout the sprawling nation. Stephanie Sy reports.]]></description>
